ackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6252af70-3b27-444f-88d0-107564cddaf5_960x720.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6252af70-3b27-444f-88d0-107564cddaf5_960x720.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6252af70-3b27-444f-88d0-107564cddaf5_960x720.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6252af70-3b27-444f-88d0-107564cddaf5_960x720.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6252af70-3b27-444f-88d0-107564cddaf5_960x720.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6252af70-3b27-444f-88d0-107564cddaf5_960x720.jpeg" width="658" height="493.5" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/6252af70-3b27-444f-88d0-107564cddaf5_960x720.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:720,&quot;width&quot;:960,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:658,&quot;bytes&quot;:270922,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6252af70-3b27-444f-88d0-107564cddaf5_960x720.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6252af70-3b27-444f-88d0-107564cddaf5_960x720.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6252af70-3b27-444f-88d0-107564cddaf5_960x720.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6252af70-3b27-444f-88d0-107564cddaf5_960x720.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源：美国宇航局</figcaption></figure></div><p>这个国家非常干燥，除了这条细细的河流沿岸之外，基本上不可能在任何地方居住。地球上没有其他国家的人口分布与埃及相似： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff66e7820-a400-4f34-b5d5-cb25516aec3b_1338x795.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff66e7820-a400-4f34-b5d5-cb25516aec3b_1338x795.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff66e7820-a400-4f34-b5d5-cb25516aec3b_1338x795.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff66e7820-a400-4f34-b5d5-cb25516aec3b_1338x795.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff66e7820-a400-4f34-b5d5-cb25516aec3b_1338x795.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff66e7820-a400-4f34-b5d5-cb25516aec3b_1338x795.jpeg" width="1338" height="795" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/f66e7820-a400-4f34-b5d5-cb25516aec3b_1338x795.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:795,&quot;width&quot;:1338,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:247738,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff66e7820-a400-4f34-b5d5-cb25516aec3b_1338x795.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff66e7820-a400-4f34-b5d5-cb25516aec3b_1338x795.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff66e7820-a400-4f34-b5d5-cb25516aec3b_1338x795.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff66e7820-a400-4f34-b5d5-cb25516aec3b_1338x795.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源：农业部</figcaption></figure></div><p>许多类型的制造业都非常耗水。对于这些人来说，埃及唯一真正的希望是利用海水淡化——海水淡化的成本正在<a href="https://www.warpnews.org/green-tech/desalination-of-salt-water-is-getting-cheaper-and-cheaper/">迅速降低</a>——并将工厂建在海岸上。廉价的太阳能会有所帮助。</p><p>但某些类型的制造业并不需要大量的水，制造业（包括建筑业）约占<a href="https://data.worldbank.org/indicator/NV.IND.MANF.ZS">埃及 GDP 的 16%</a>就证明了这一点——就国家而言，这个比例相当高。因此，缺乏水资源并不一定是一个问题。</p><p>第二个障碍是<strong>教育水平</strong>低。以现代标准衡量，埃及的识字率相当低，约为 75%： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59992d26-a7b4-4a45-aed4-14adb5a30190_1020x720.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59992d26-a7b4-4a45-aed4-14adb5a30190_1020x720.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59992d26-a7b4-4a45-aed4-14adb5a30190_1020x720.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59992d26-a7b4-4a45-aed4-14adb5a30190_1020x720.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59992d26-a7b4-4a45-aed4-14adb5a30190_1020x720.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59992d26-a7b4-4a45-aed4-14adb5a30190_1020x720.jpeg" width="1020" height="720" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/59992d26-a7b4-4a45-aed4-14adb5a30190_1020x720.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:720,&quot;width&quot;:1020,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:131508,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59992d26-a7b4-4a45-aed4-14adb5a30190_1020x720.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59992d26-a7b4-4a45-aed4-14adb5a30190_1020x720.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59992d26-a7b4-4a45-aed4-14adb5a30190_1020x720.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59992d26-a7b4-4a45-aed4-14adb5a30190_1020x720.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>制造商需要能读写的工人。一开始这不是问题，因为埃及有很多识字<em>的</em>人，而且中学入学率实际上<a href="https://data.worldbank.org/indicator/SE.SEC.ENRR?locations=EG">相当不错</a>。但从长远来看，任何外国直接投资的推动都需要更多的教育支出。</p><p>第三个问题是<strong>腐败</strong>，我的出租车司机对此深感不满。埃及在腐败措施方面得分很低，尽管它远不是最差的国家之一。关键问题是<a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/egypts-military-is-under-pressure-to-loosen-its-grip-on-economy-b77d935d">军方拥有或控制着</a>该国的许多企业。这类似于20世纪末的印度尼西亚军队，或者今天的伊朗革命卫队。对商业的军事控制排挤了私营部门，而且由于缺乏竞争而常常效率低下。</p><p>尽管解决这个问题是一项长期挑战，但它并不一定会阻碍外国直接投资或制造业的增长。外国拥有的公司将没有军事所有权，在<a href="https://www.oecd-ilibrary.org/sites/8a873381-en/index.html?itemId=/content/component/8a873381-en">2017年埃及开始成立的</a>经济特区中，外国公司将受到轻易征税。这将使外国直接投资与军事竞争和提取。军队不太可能介意。他们将仅仅从流入其余埃及经济的收入中获得很大的推动力，从而使他们已经拥有的面向国内的企业受益。</p><p>这就是印度尼西亚的军事独裁者苏哈托（Suharto）的政治生涯与埃尔西西（El-Sisi）的政治生涯有一定的相似之处，他能够在80年代和90年代设计基于外国直接投资的制造业繁荣，即使他的军事部队仍然控制着许多经济的许多人。 El-Sisi应该有意识地尝试复制Suharto的经济战略。</p><p>但是，现在对埃及的最大危险不是腐败，文盲或缺水，而是外债。埃及的国内储蓄率很低 - 仅占<a href="https://data.worldbank.org/indicator/NY.GNS.ICTR.ZS?most_recent_value_desc=true">国内生产总值的13％</a> - 因此它无法真正为其所做的所有基础设施支出提供资金。取而代之的是，它在很大程度上<a href="https://www.reuters.com/world/africa/egypt-faces-external-debt-reckoning-after-borrowing-spree-2023-06-06/">从国外借了钱</a>。但是埃及不能用埃及磅借钱。它必须借入美元或欧元或其他外币。</p><p>这使埃及处于巨大的危险中。请记住，<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/why-sri-lanka-is-having-an-economic">经典的新兴市场危机</a>是如何运作的 - 一个国家借用了一堆以外国货币为主导的债务，然后其货币货币造成价值，使其无法偿还其债务。然后，它要么违约或打印资金并承受过度通货膨胀，这两者都将经济送入了尾速（尽管过度充电更糟）。埃及尤其面临这种危机的危险，因为它持续存在贸易赤字。这是<a href="https://www.reuters.com/world/africa/egypt-faces-external-debt-reckoning-after-borrowing-spree-2023-06-06/">路透社的故事</a>：</p><blockquote><p> [埃及政府]的大项目中，很少有人会产生额外的硬货币流入……全球借贷成本已经上涨了……在外币紧缩中，埃及在两年内将银行体系中的净外国资产降低了400亿美元，部分使用了支撑英镑……硬货币紧缩引起了人们对埃及偿还外债能力的<a href="https://www.reuters.com/world/africa/north-africa-backslides-toward-swirling-debt-troubles-2023-05-11/">担忧</a>。自4月以来，所有三个主要信贷机构都降低了埃及债务的前景… </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8f5c71df-b8c2-419f-a967-ff57bff3ef65_891x585.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8f5c71df-b8c2-419f-a967-ff57bff3ef65_891x585.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8f5c71df-b8c2-419f-a967-ff57bff3ef65_891x585.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8f5c71df-b8c2-419f-a967-ff57bff3ef65_891x585.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8f5c71df-b8c2-419f-a967-ff57bff3ef65_891x585.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8f5c71df-b8c2-419f-a967-ff57bff3ef65_891x585.jpeg" width="891" height="585" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/8f5c71df-b8c2-419f-a967-ff57bff3ef65_891x585.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:585,&quot;width&quot;:891,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:79002,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8f5c71df-b8c2-419f-a967-ff57bff3ef65_891x585.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8f5c71df-b8c2-419f-a967-ff57bff3ef65_891x585.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8f5c71df-b8c2-419f-a967-ff57bff3ef65_891x585.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8f5c71df-b8c2-419f-a967-ff57bff3ef65_891x585.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div></blockquote><p>货币危机和违约绝对会使埃及的增长故事陷入尾巴，并导致大规模的国内动荡，因为普通的埃及人无法负担进口的小麦。埃及非常<a href="https://www.mdpi.com/2077-0472/13/1/7">依赖进口的小麦</a>，这就是为什么当全球食品价格上涨时，您总是听到埃及面包暴动的原因。如果埃及有货币危机，El-Sisi的统治显然将处于危险之中。</p><p>政府知道危险。一月份，具有大量外国资金的基础设施项目<a href="https://www.reuters.com/world/africa/egypt-orders-ministries-curb-spending-amid-foreign-currency-crunch-2023-01-10/">被暂停</a>。但这只是一个开始。政府将需要争先恐后地提出足够的外币，以在未来两年内偿还其外债。</p><p>但是，即使埃及努力避免债务违约，它也需要长期重新定位其经济。外国直接投资和出口应该是明确的目标。为此，埃及政府应该做以下操作：</p><ul><li><p>围绕SEZ的混凝土需求而不是浮华的大型项目，东方基础设施支出</p></li><li><p>提高国内储蓄率，以免依靠外国借贷</p></li><li><p>在教育上花费更多</p></li><li><p>以<a href="https://www.oecd-ilibrary.org/sites/8a873381-en/index.html?itemId=/content/component/8a873381-en">其他各种方式</a>改善经济特区政策</p></li></ul><p>我知道对埃及保持乐观并不时尚 - 而我的出租车司机当然不是 - 但我相信他们可以做到这一点。他们已经证明自己是中东最稳定，最和平的国家之一，他们在没有大量自然资源的情况下取得了中等水平的收入水平，并且他们表明他们愿意在基础设施上花费很多钱。对于一个成功的工业化故事，这些作品还没有到位，但其中一些是政府的，政府知道增长是唯一能使人民开心的东西。当然，埃及有很多问题，但对我来说，这看起来并不像是绝望的篮子。 </p><div><hr></div><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/subscribe?&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Subscribe now&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"><a class="button primary" href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/subscribe?"><span>现在订阅</span></a></p><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/feeling-strangely-optimistic-about?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=share&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Share&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"> <a class="button primary" href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/feeling-strangely-optimistic-about?utm