thout having the city start to look like a ruin in a jungle (like <a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/taipei-urbanism">parts of Taipei</a> ). All that foliage must be landscaped, and that&#39;s never cheap. So Singapore&#39;s gorgeous greenery is really a spectacular demonstration of wealth.</p><p> In fact, the greenery isn&#39;t just <em>around</em> the buildings; it&#39;s <em>in</em> them too. Singapore leads the world in “ <a href="https://www.vagabondjourney.com/plants-on-buildings-skyrise-greenery-in-singapore/">skyrise greenery</a> ” — ie, covering the exteriors of its towers with foliage. </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1aed804f-6d86-4061-8a55-0fc50f69c989_1024x771.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1aed804f-6d86-4061-8a55-0fc50f69c989_1024x771.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1aed804f-6d86-4061-8a55-0fc50f69c989_1024x771.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1aed804f-6d86-4061-8a55-0fc50f69c989_1024x771.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1aed804f-6d86-4061-8a55-0fc50f69c989_1024x771.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_p